Indirect/Frostbringer/After moving to a tile, all Enemies along the same horizontal line as the Frost Knight are frozen. Freeze: Enemy is stunned and if killed while frozen, deals 2 damage to all adjacent enemies.

Direct/Ice Bash/Shove a Piece 1 tile away and freeze it if it's an Enemy. If the shoved Piece lands on another Piece, deal 4 damage to it. Shoving a Piece off the top, left, and right edges of the map kills it.